[02:30] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'So, does it work? Yes! It works spectacularly. Finally, we have someone writing the manual, and of course, at the end of the chain, the user installing the game, running it, and evaluating it.'

[02:44] [scene:talk]
